us/2071398613700534688", "text": "US interest rates up tonight.\n\nUS 10 yr up to 4.3803% in tonight's trading to 8:55pm ET.  US 10 yr was down to 4.3686% to close on 06/26.\n\nUS 2 yr up to 4.1045% in tonight's trading to 8:59pm ET.  US 2 yr was down to  4.0921% to close on 06/26.\n\nThx @business #oott", "time": "01:01", "author": "Energy_Tidbits", "author_name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "views": 3487, "likes": 4, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071438678665077028", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071438678665077028", "text": "Putin says Russia faces fuel shortages as Ukrainian drones strike refineries\nPresident’s comments are first admission that Kyiv’s long-range attacks have dented production\n#oott https://t.co/Z2y4gcewjV", "time": "03:40", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3637, "likes": 15, "replies": 4, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Russia sanctions", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2071454350061224140", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071454350061224140", "text": "Russia's Putin acknowledges fuel shortages, task force set up to ensure supplies #oott https://t.co/VaxCpUl3gu", "time": "04:42", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3945, "likes": 8, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Russia sanctions", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2071474363707109691", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071474363707109691", "text": "Brent futures curve in USD/bbl (today, one week ago and one month ago) #OOTT https://t.co/PMNxd9zkfK", "time"