ment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071528156482228678", "url": "https://x.com/PetroleumEcon/status/2071528156482228678", "text": "The geological #hydrogen sector is starting to attract significant venture capital, although comparisons with the development of upstream #gas look premature #OOTT #energy\nhttps://t.co/TEh5nSbOn7 https://t.co/iNKQlZMCTx", "time": "09:36", "author": "PetroleumEcon", "author_name": "Petroleum Economist", "followers": 67133, "views": 1197, "likes": 19, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Natural gas"]}}, {"id": "2071537206351868239", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2071537206351868239", "text": "That’s why oil prices aren’t rising yet (MM are currently holding a historically high number of short positions, dreaming for a quick SoH reopening )\nBut this could change dramatically within coming days\n#oott #Iran #Hormuz https://t.co/dEPTqI6VU0", "time": "10:12", "author": "Amalteya3000", "author_name": "Amalteya", "followers": 773, "views": 2698, "likes": 46, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2071576046567035033", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2071576046567035033", "text": "White House says U.S. negotiators will travel to Doha, the Qatari capital, for talks with Iranian officials tomorrow. President Trump said: “Iran has requested a meeting.”", "time": "12:46", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 40242, "likes": 101, "replies": 22, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2071590681882116251", "url": "https://x.com/IliaBouchouev/status/2071590681882116251", "text": "With inventories impossible to track now, traders increasingly rely on curve dynamics as a proxy for forward s&amp;d expectations. This \"deceleration of backwardation\" signal (curve-momentum) turned decidely bearish and is behind the recent wave of selling.\n#oott https://t.co/pYz9eUzoFD", "time": "13:44", "author": "IliaBouchouev", "author_name": "Dr. Ilia Bouchouev", "followers": 19952, "views": 14102, "likes": 68, "replies": 7, "retweets": 17, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 26, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071606521276899329", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2071606521276899329", "text": "Spent some time with CNBC's @TheDomino on Friday talking the Iran situation - oil price is weak sentiment over decent fundamentals (inventory), strong US desire to get a deal (despite Hormuz strikes) and better floor price going forward ($75+) #EFT #OOTT\n\nhttps://t.co/Y8hDI8rqSa", "time": "14:47", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 4917, "likes": 17, "replies": 22, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071626882840203673", "url": "https://x.com/th_gambler/status/2071626882840203673", "text": "So the actual SoH recovery isn’t that big because out of 14mbpd over 6mbpd are getting exported through the red sea. So SoH recovery is what, 8mbpd? @Rory_Johnston \n\nthank you again for the Data\n\n#oott", "time": "16:08", "author": "th_gambler", "author_name": "TheRealGambler", "followers": 343, "views": 4877, "likes": 21, "replies": 2, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071642010201559263", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071642010201559263", "text": "Rig explosion in #Venezuela leaves at least 8 workers injured, sources say #oott https://t.co/bPANSn6YZt", "time": "17:08", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 5691, "likes": 12, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Venezuela", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2071642954632921559", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071642954632921559", "text": "US SPR crude inventories fell by ~5.5mb w/w to a multi year low of 325.7mb last week #oott      \n\nSour down ~2.7mb to 205.5mb    \nSweet down ~2.9mb to 120.9mb https://t.co/gnv7sJziwf", "time": "17:12", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 82885, "likes": 174, "replies": 22, "retweets": 37, "quotes": 8, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2071661460585914619", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2071661460585914619", "text": "Iran Deputy Foreign Minister: Iran Opposes, Will Try To Obstruct Any Vessels Transiting Through Paths In Hormuz Not Specified By Tehran\n\n#OOTT", "time": "18:25", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436344, "views": 14514, "likes": 11, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2071661663133081807", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071661663133081807", "text": "#Iran opposes and will try to obstruct any vessels transiting through paths in Hormuz not specified by Iran - deputy FM Gharibabadi #oott", "time": "18:26", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6659, "likes": 30, "replies": 2, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2071662893133693040", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2071662893133693040", "text": "WTI settled at USD 70.75/bbl #oott", "time": "18:31", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4751, "likes": 24, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2071664652862341491", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2071664652862341491", "text": "Chinese state-owned oil trader Unipec offered today a key North Sea crude oil at its widest discount to the Dated Brent benchmark in six years (during the peak of the Covid lockdowns in April 2020). Beijing’s oil buying strike continued.", "time": "18:38", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 127720, "likes": 440, "replies": 17, "retweets": 51, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 66, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand"]}}, {"id": "2071667084023521397", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2071667084023521397", "text": "Both the American and the Iranian delegations have decided to visit Doha at the same time of a very sunny day of the Persian Gulf summer. Truly, a coincidence this all happened.", "time": "18:48", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 68215, "likes": 436, "replies": 22, "retweets": 57, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 22, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Gio